{"text_id":258906,"tokens":["In"," this"," work",","," we"," present"," a"," novel"," method"," for"," matched"," filtering"," numerical"," relativity"," templates"," of"," spinning"," binary"," black"," holes","."," We"," focus"," on"," the"," development"," of"," an"," efficient"," and"," accurate"," approach"," for"," detecting"," gravitational"," wave"," signals"," arising"," from"," these"," sources","."," The"," concept"," behind"," matched"," filtering"," is"," to"," correlate"," the"," gravitational"," wave"," signal"," with"," a"," set"," of"," templates"," whose"," signals"," bear"," the"," closest"," resemblance"," to"," the"," predicted"," signals","."," Our"," methodology"," is"," based"," on"," using"," a"," Fourier"," domain"," version"," of"," the"," stationary"," phase"," approximation"," as"," a"," means"," of"," calculating"," the"," correlation"," between"," the"," data"," and"," a"," family"," of"," time","-","domain"," waveforms","."," This"," technique"," offers"," a"," significant"," reduction"," in"," computational"," cost"," while"," maintaining"," a"," high"," level"," of"," accuracy","."," ","\n\n","We"," illustrate"," our"," method"," using"," numerical"," relativity"," waveforms",","," and"," we"," show"," that"," our"," approach"," can"," recover"," the"," correct"," parameters"," with"," high"," precision"," for"," both"," non","-","spinning"," and"," spinning"," binary"," black"," holes","."," With"," our"," matched"," filtering"," technique",","," we"," can"," extract"," gravitational"," wave"," signals"," from"," black"," hole"," mergers"," and"," estimate"," the"," parameters"," of"," the"," merger"," accurately",","," providing"," valuable"," information"," about"," the"," underlying"," physics"," involved","."," ","\n\n","This"," research"," is"," motivated"," by"," the"," need"," to"," study"," and"," understand"," the"," properties"," of"," binary"," black"," hole"," mergers"," and"," their"," implications"," for"," astro","physics","."," The"," detection"," of"," gravitational"," waves"," from"," these"," mergers"," provides"," us"," with"," a"," unique"," opportunity"," to"," explore"," the"," properties"," of"," black"," holes"," and"," the"," dynamics"," of"," gravity"," in"," extreme"," environments","."," Our"," new"," matched"," filtering"," approach"," will"," help"," us"," maximize"," the"," scientific"," yield"," of"," gravitational"," wave"," detections",","," making"," it"," possible"," to"," extract"," a"," wealth"," of"," information"," about"," black"," hole"," systems","."],"sub_source":"arxiv","model":"gpt-3.5-turbo","label":1}